SQL_STMT_U.val: select T5.PrcName as 'Jenis', T0.NumAtCard as 'No Pendaftaran', T1.GTSRegNum as 'No RM', T6.CardName as 'Tipe Pasien', T0.DocDate as 'Tanggal Pulang', T0.Cardname as 'Nama Pasien', T3.Comments as 'Nama Pelayanan', T4.Acctname as 'Nama Dokter', T4.SumApplied as 'Jasmed' from OINV T0 (nolock) left Join OCRD T1 on T0.CardCode=T1.CardCode --T1.GTSRegNum IS NOT NULL and left join OCRD T6 on T0.BPChCode = t6.CardCode left join INV1 T2 on T0.DocEntry=T1.DocEntry left join ORCT T3 on T0.NumAtCard=T3.CounterRef and T3.DocType='A' join RCT4 T4 on T3.DocEntry=T4.DocNum left join OPRC T5 on T0.U_IDU_Kode_PT=T5.PrcCode where t0.DocSubType = '--' and T0.CANCELED='N' and T0.DocStatus='C' and T0.DocDate between :1 and :2 and ISNULL(T0.NumAtCard,'') LIKE :3 and ISNULL(T4.AcctName,'') LIKE :4 and ISNULL(T1.GTSRegNum,'') LIKE :5
